This is a PHP example on how to use Pwned Platform.

DOCUMENTATION: http://api.pwned.com/docs
REQUIREMENTS:
	-OAuth Pecl Library
		- http://pecl.php.net/package/oauth

This is a pretty straight forward example on how to use the Pecl OAuth library to make connections and access data through the API.

HOW TO CREATE AN APPLICATION
1) Register or Login to your Pwned.com account
2) Go to http://api.pwned.com
3) Create the application at http://api.pwned.com/newapp
4) Fill out the required fields
5) Redirects back and displays Consumer Secret/Consumer Key (save these keys)
6) Use the example here to test :D

RESOURCES: http://pwned.com/forums/viewforum.php?f=41

